file.name: links_by_user_id.yml
file.content:
Return public user links (You can provide specific date to get all links created after that date)
---
openapi: 3.0.0
components:
  securitySchemes:
    bearerAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
      bearerFormat: JWT
security:
  - bearerAuth: []
consumes:
  "application/json"
tags:
  - name: "Links"
parameters:
  - in: header
    name: Authorization
    description: "Send like this: Bearer [TOKEN]"
    type: string
    required: true
  - name: "id"
    in: "path"
    description: "User id to get"
    required: true
    type: "integer"
  - name: "page"
    in: "query"
    description: "Which page do want to get"
    required: false
    type: "integer"
  - name: "page_size"
    in: "query"
    description: "the number of links in each page"
    required: false
    type: "integer"
  - name: body
    in: body
    required: true
    schema:
      properties:
        date_from:
          type: string
          description: "Starting date with this format: YYYY-MM-DD hh:mm `Not Required`"
          example: "2020-12-05 19:12"

responses:
  200:
    description: "Return bookmarks"
    schema:
      type: object
      properties:
        categories:
          type: array
          items:
            type: object
            properties:
              id:
                type: integer
              name:
                type: string
          description: "Link related categories"
        url:
          type: string
          description: "Link url"
        id:
          type: int
          description: "Id of link"
        added_date:
          type: string
          description: "Date that link is added in format `YYYY-MM-DD hh:mm`"
      example:
        categories: [
          {"id": 1, "name": "programming"},
          {"id": 5, "name": "searching"},
          {"id": 11, "name": "Q and A"}
        ]
        url: https://stackoverflow.com
        id: 2
        added_date: "2020-12-07 12:28"
  400:
    description: "Input date does not match format 'YYYY-MM-DD hh:mm' OR Requested page size is larger than our max limit!"
    schema:
      type: object
      properties:
        msg:
          type: string
          description: "Input date does not match format 'YYYY-MM-DD hh:mm' OR Requested page size is larger than our max limit!"
      example:
        msg: "Input date does not match format 'YYYY-MM-DD hh:mm'"
  403:
    description: User is not public!
    schema:
      type: object
      properties:
        msg:
          type: string
          description: User is not public!
      example:
        msg: User is not public!
  404:
    description: User not found! OR Link not found!
    schema:
      type: object
      properties:
        msg:
          type: string
          description: User not found! OR Link not found!
      example:
        msg: User not found!
